</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Embedding模型 → 将问题转为向量 Query-Vector
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">向量数据库检索 → 找出Top-K相似的文档片段
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">构建Prompt: 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  &#34;基于以下信息回答问题：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   [文档片段1] [文档片段2] [文档片段3]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   问题：公司的年假政策是什么？&#34;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">LLM生成回答</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>RAG vs 微调</strong>：</p>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>维度</th>
          <th>RAG</th>
          <th>微调</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>知识更新</td>
